(In reply to Matt from comment #12)
Ok!

4. Better use tarball from upstream (MASTER_SITES) instead of USE_GITHUB=yes.

5. I would change it like this:
MASTER_SITES=	https://github.com/${PORTNAME}/${PORTNAME}/releases/download/${DISTVERSION}/
USE_RC_SUBR=	${PORTNAME}
USERS=		_${PORTNAME}
GROUPS=		_${PORTNAME}
        @${MKDIR} ${STAGEDIR}${PYTHONPREFIX_SITELIBDIR}/${PORTNAME}
        cd ${WRKSRC}/${PORTNAME} && ${COPYTREE_SHARE} . ${STAGEDIR}${PYTHONPREFIX_SITELIBDIR}/${PORTNAME}

6. NO_BUILD=yes after NO_ARCH=yes.

7. Added %%NLS%% should not change the sorting in pkg-plist.

8. %%DATADIR%%/email/email-*.tmpl are installed even without the NLS option.
If you want you can remove files in post-install-NLS-off.
